        public void buyUpgradeClicked​(javafx.event.ActionEvent e)
        This method handle the event when buyUpgrade-button is clicked. It checks if you owns all the properties within a street, or if the property already has max upgrades.
        Parameters:

      • sellClicked

        public void sellClicked​(javafx.event.ActionEvent e)
        This method handle the event when sell-button is clicked. It checks if you have any upgrades to sell, and if not it sells the property itself.
        Parameters:
        e - Event when buyUpgrade-button is clicked.
